data.description: Move-in Ready, End unit maintenance-free patio style townhome in a quiet peaceful 55+ community in a park-like setting. Beautifully updated kitchen with custom cabinets, large pantry, convenient pass-through counter to the dining room, and engineered hardwood floors, featuring updated appliances. New Furnace and AC in 2020, New 50-gallon Water Heater in 2021 so that you can enjoy soaking in the deep jetted walk-in tub! Active Radon System is installed. Immaculate well-maintained super comfortable worry-free living for your golden years! The HOA maintains the exterior of each townhome building including cleaning gutters, snow removal when 2" or more, and all the lawns. This is a very coveted Senior Community, so don't delay scheduling your tour!
